getReader

@Deprecated
public DatasetReader<E> getReader()
Deprecated. 

Description copied from interface: Dataset

Get an appropriate DatasetReader implementation based on the underlying Dataset implementation.

Implementations are free to return different types of readers depending on the disposition of the data. For example, a partitioned dataset may use a different reader than that of a non-partitioned dataset. Clients should not make any assumptions about the returned implementations. Dataset implementations are free to change them at any time.
